The X Factor - Series 12, Episode 15




Live Show #1

The 12 remaining acts compete for the chance to make it through to the live final later this year. The theme for this weekend is 'This Is Me', with each act performing a song that reflects the identity they would assume should they make it in the music business. Plus, 2014 winner Ben Haenow returns to the show to perform his debut single Second Hand Heart.




Original Air Date: 31-Oct-2015
